This Dokuwiki plugin automatically creates user and log them in at Zenphoto. When a user changed, the changes are applied to Zenphotos user database as well. It provides a single signed on mechanism as well.

Requirements:
  * Zenphoto installation
  * Dokuwiki installation

Usage:
  * Unzip to your Dokuwiki lib/plugins directory
  * Login to your Dokuwiki and visit your admin page
  * Edit zenlogin options according to your Zenphoto configuration
  * Register user and watch them appear in your Zenphoto installation

Visit http://blog.falstaff.ch/2010/08/17/zenphoto-dokuwiki-integration/ for 
more information
